OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAnimal shelter sees rise in
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcats being given up        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More cats are being handed to animal   
OL,6, shelters due to the cost of living     
OL,7, crisis, a charity has said.            
OL,9,FFigures from the Cats Protection       
OL,10,Fcharity's adoption centre in Wrexham   
OL,11,Fshow that one in five cats brought to  
OL,12,Fthe centre were due to their owners    
OL,13,Fbeing unable to afford their upkeep.   
OL,15,FThe increase in numbers has prompted an
OL,16,Fappeal for volunteers to help socialise
OL,17,Fthe abandoned felines with cuddles.    
OL,19,FCats Protection in Wales said it was a 
OL,20,Fsimilar picture across Wales.          
